OL,3,CMan who discarded single cigarette
OL,4,Cbutt outside shops fined over #1600
OL,6,FA man who discarded a single cigarette
OL,7,Fbutt outside a parade of shops in
OL,8,FBuckinghamshire has been forced to pay
OL,9,Fover #1,600 in court.
OL,11,FArthur McCann, from Northwich Road in
OL,12,FWatford, was convicted of littering.
OL,14,FWycombe Magistrates' Court heard that
OL,15,Fon 25 February 2025, a cigarette butt
OL,16,Fwas dropped outside the parade of
OL,17,Fshops in Little Chalfont.
OL,19,FCouncil litter enforcement officers
OL,20,Fsaw the offence and issued a Fixed
OL,21,FPenalty Notice (FPN) of #500.
