OL,6,FMcCann chose not to pay the penalty
OL,7,Fand so the council reviewed the case
OL,8,Fand submitted it for prosecution.
OL,10,FIn court, Magistrates fined McCann
OL,11,F#500 and ordered him to pay
OL,12,Fprosecution costs of #941.16. A victim
OL,13,Fsurcharge of #200 was also levied,
OL,14,Fmaking a total to pay of #1,641.16.
