OL,6,FCarl Jackson, Buckinghamshire
OL,7,FCouncil's Cabinet Member for
OL,8,FEnvironment, Climate Change & Waste
OL,9,Fsaid: "This case sends the message
OL,10,Floud and clear that Buckinghamshire
OL,11,FCouncil takes a zero-tolerance
OL,12,Fapproach to littering.
OL,14,F"Anyone caught littering will be
OL,15,Fissued with a #500 Fixed Penalty
OL,16,FNotice.
OL,18,F"If that person chooses to ignore the
OL,19,Fnotice, they could end up facing
OL,20,Fprosecution and paying much more.
